<h1> My favorite song...

i := 99
s := "s"

<#bottles>
    while i > 0
        if i == 1 do s = "" else do s = "s"
        <p> "{i} bottle{s} of beer on the wall,"
        <p> "{i} bottle{s} of beer!"
        <p> Take one down, pass it around...
        i -= 1
        if i > 0
            if i == 1 do s = "" else do s = "s"
            <p> "{i} bottle{s} of beer on the wall!"

    <p> No more bottles of beer on the wall!
